1937;;Night Key;;American;;Lloyd Corrigan;;Boris Karloff, Jean Rogers, Alan Baxter;;drama, crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Night_Key;;The inventor of a burglar alarm (Karloff) attempts to get back at the man who stole the profits to his invention (Hinds) before he goes blind. The device is then subverted by gangsters (Baxter, et al.) who apply pressure to the inventor and use his device to facilitate burglaries.